message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you for $9,500. I think it's a fair price considering its value.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate your willingness to sell the product. I would like to counteroffer at $9,000 for the product.
Thanks for the offer, Bob. I understand your position, but I'm looking for something closer to $9,300. It's still a great deal for you considering its value.
I appreciate your response, Alice. Considering the value of the product and my budget, I would like to counteroffer at $9,100.
